1
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:04,419
Even in Tokyo, there are places like this.

2
00:00:04,420 --> 00:00:07,720
I know. It was worth coming, right?

3
00:00:08,820 --> 00:00:11,219
The air's clear and the view's excellent.

4
00:00:11,220 --> 00:00:13,619
What a great place to drink sake.

5
00:00:13,620 --> 00:00:16,020
This way, please.

6
00:00:19,420 --> 00:00:23,419
Hey, miss. That watermill isn't working.

7
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:26,319
That's right. It used to deliver water

8
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,519
to the wasabi farms.

9
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:31,419
Now we use it as an icehouse.

10
00:00:31,420 --> 00:00:33,819
An icehouse?

11
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:36,519
That's like a natural refrigerator, right?

12
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,619
Yes.

13
00:00:37,620 --> 00:00:41,619
It's where we keep the natural ice we serve here.

14
00:00:41,620 --> 00:00:42,920
Excuse me.

15
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:47,419
"Juri Matsui, Maria Suzumoto, Yuko Akiba (21)" -Are you...

16
00:00:47,420 --> 00:00:49,320
"Teito University Philosophy Student" -Mr. Kogoro Mouri?

17
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:53,019
Yes, that's me.

18
00:00:53,020 --> 00:00:56,519
May I take a photo with you?

19
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:59,019
Of course. I don't mind.

20
00:00:59,020 --> 00:01:01,219
Why don't I take it for you?

21
00:01:01,220 --> 00:01:02,920
No, thank you.

22
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,619
Over here.

23
00:01:08,620 --> 00:01:10,519
Let's line up in front of the river.

24
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:13,320
Mr. Mouri, everyone, please.

25
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:16,120
Come on, Maria.

26
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,020
Here.

27
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,819
Wait. Move aside.

28
00:01:23,820 --> 00:01:24,920
Yuko.

29
00:01:28,020 --> 00:01:29,519
Here we go.

30
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:31,619
Okay. Say "cheese".

31
00:01:31,620 --> 00:01:33,020
Cheese...

32
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:38,519
When the countdown reaches zero,

33
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:41,120
