34
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,119
Taking a commemorate photo by a cool riverbed.

35
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,519
Do these three women even like each other?

36
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,019
He sees through the one and only truth.

37
00:01:49,020 --> 00:01:50,819
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

38
00:01:50,820 --> 00:01:52,920
His name is Detective Conan!

39
00:03:31,256 --> 00:03:34,356
"Friendship Washed Away In The Riverbed"

40
00:03:36,756 --> 00:03:40,455
Gosh! I have a blister.

41
00:03:40,456 --> 00:03:43,755
I'm exhausted from walking so far.

42
00:03:43,756 --> 00:03:46,655
But you said you wanted to come here.

43
00:03:46,656 --> 00:03:48,455
Isn't that because you suggested

44
00:03:48,456 --> 00:03:51,555
