45
00:03:51,556 --> 00:03:53,355
Now, now.

46
00:03:53,356 --> 00:03:56,256
We came here to make up with each other.

47
00:03:59,156 --> 00:04:02,156
Maria, do you have any band-aids?

48
00:04:06,456 --> 00:04:07,756
Thanks.

49
00:04:08,656 --> 00:04:10,556
Excuse me.

50
00:04:13,156 --> 00:04:15,855
Here is your appetizer.

51
00:04:15,856 --> 00:04:17,755
This looks delicious!

52
00:04:17,756 --> 00:04:19,956
I'll take one, too.

53
00:04:22,256 --> 00:04:24,356
What are they doing?

54
00:04:25,256 --> 00:04:27,255
Dad, don't you know?

55
00:04:27,256 --> 00:04:29,355
