65
00:05:00,456 --> 00:05:03,055
You never change.

66
00:05:03,056 --> 00:05:04,555
How about mine?

67
00:05:04,556 --> 00:05:08,555
Maria showed me a new app.

68
00:05:08,556 --> 00:05:09,955
It's all right.

69
